                                                                    <tr>
                                                                        <td style="margin: 0; padding: 13px 10px 10px 0; display: none; width: 0;"></td>
                                                                        <td valign="top" width="100%" style="font-weight: 600; color: #979797; font-size: 11px; line-height: 13px; padding: 13px 10px">PROBABILITY OF &ge; 1 INFECTED TRAVELLER*<br /><span style="color: #AE9F7E">(Change from last week)</span></td>
